{"service_name": "Sopra Steria Design Authority", "service_id": "7325402953463026", "company_name": "Sopra Steria Ltd", "page_content": "<main id=\"content\" role=\"main\">\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <header class=\"page-heading-smaller\">\n    <p class=\"context\">\n     Sopra Steria Ltd\n    </p>\n    <h1>\n     Sopra Steria Design Authority\n    </h1>\n   </header>\n  </div>\n </div>\n <div class=\"grid-row\">\n  <div class=\"column-two-thirds\">\n   <p class=\"service-summary-lede\">\n    As public sector organisations address the Digital and Cloud agenda there is an increasing awareness that agile delivery and disruptive technologies do not remove the need for governance and technical oversight. We recognise the need for a strong Technical Design Authority (TDA) within the context of Government Cloud strategy.\n   </p>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Features\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Adoption of the Government Digital Service (GDS) strategy\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Expertise on Transition of existing applications into the Cloud\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Integration of PaaS and SaaS applications into end-to-end designs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Transform applications into re-usable IT assets\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Extend the life of legacy applications through Cloud technologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Building new interfaces with greater interoperability\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Ensuring that quality of service is maintained\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <h2 class=\"service-summary-heading\">\n    Benefits\n   </h2>\n   <ul class=\"service-summary-features-and-benefits\">\n    <li>\n     Alignment of business case to business value of strategic initiatives\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Exploitation / integration of emerging technologies\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Exploitation of Agile delivery approaches\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Enable reuse and time savings wherever possible\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Lower cost - support, running and acquisition costs\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Increased flexibility\n    </li>\n    <li>\n     Governance and control\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n  </div>\n  <div class=\"column-one-third\">\n   <div id=\"meta\">\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Pricing\n    </h2>\n    <p class=\"price\">\n     \u00a3675 per person per day\n    </p>\n    <ul class=\"price-caveats\">\n     <li>\n      Excluding VAT\n     </li>\n     <li>\n      Minimum contract period: Day\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n    <h2 class=\"visuallyhidden\">\n     Service documents\n    </h2>\n    <ul class=\"document-list\">\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700976/7325402953463026-pricing-document-2015-10-02-1329.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Pricing\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700976/7325402953463026-sfia-rate-card-2015-10-02-1329.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       SFIA rate card\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.gov.uk/g-cloud-7/documents/700976/7325402953463026-service-definition-document-2015-10-05-1543.pdf\">\n       <span class=\"document-icon\">\n        pdf\n        <span>\n         document:\n        </span>\n       </span>\n       Service definition\n      </a>\n     </li>\n     <li class=\"document-list-item\">\n      <a class=\"document-link-with-icon\" href=\"https://assets.digitalmarketplace.service.